Twitter Job Bot
by Daniel Haran

Description

https://twitter.com/jobbot/

  DM me with location (L:mycity) and keywords (e.g. senior developer) for jobs you want to hear about. 
  I DM you as soon as they are published.

Details / Implementation checklist

-subscribe to all tweets hash-tagged #jobs
-send new followers command info
-listen to DM
-send appropriately filtered DMs

